vote.title: Authorize (1) a Standard Utility Agreement with the State of Texas, acting through the Texas Department of Transportation, for water pipeline encasement extensions in State Highway 205 from FM 548 to US 80; and (2) the receipt and deposit of funds from the Texas Department of Transportation for reimbursement of eligible construction, inspection, and project management costs for the project - Estimated Revenue: Dallas Water Utilities Fund $123,165.67
